schools.name: Boerne - Samuel V Champion High School

data.description: NEW ROOF and all NEW CARPET!  Experience Small Town Charm with Big City Access! Nestled in the coveted Boerne school district, you'll enjoy top-rated schools and easy highway access for a stress-free commute into San Antonio. This lovely home is situated a stone's throw away from Boerne Middle School South and Kendall Elementary School, making the morning school run a breeze. Plus, you're just moments away from a variety of restaurants and even a movie theatre for family entertainment. The home boasts a primary bedroom on the main level for added convenience, and the fully fenced backyard provides a secure space for outdoor activities. With gas cooking and heating, you'll experience efficiency and reliability year-round. Inside, you'll find an open and spacious layout that's perfect for gatherings and quality family time. This is the ideal place to call home, offering both comfort and accessibility. Schedule your showing today and experience the best of Boerne living with all the conveniences of nearby San Antonio.
